name: I Dream of Jack-O-Laterns -2007 (Re-release) - Pre-Order
description:
( PRE-ORDER ONLY) 25 AVAILABLE - FIRST COME FIRST SERVED - SHIPS AUGUST 31ST 2010 
Discontinued since 2008. The Coffin Caddies debut release "I Dream of Jack-O-Lanterns" has been a must have by fans of Horror Punk and Pop punk genre's.  This album contains 16 ghoulish tracks covering every theme from Spider man to Zombies ate my neighbors. Pre-order this re-release before the limited supply runs out.
